# Walk-swap + myitem regression (synthetic, v2 format). Two workers holding
# out-of-order values must swap positions (both step toward each other) so the
# row reads sorted. Exercises: ent lines, pickup s, myitem vs tile comparison,
# the mutual-swap movement rule, and the sorted-row win check.
name Swap Sort
dim 4 3
ent wall 0 0
ent worker 1 1
ent worker 2 1
ent cube 1 2 9
ent cube 2 2 3
goal sorted_row_holdable
